description: My secretary brought me a lovely cutie as a first thing in the morning. He was very chatty and nice. Maybe his haircut was a bit wild to my taste but why not. He used to work in finance so he was more than capable to do the math when I told him about the job and made my usual offer. I thought he will agree but he wanted some time to think it through and left. The next guy wore a huddle. A huddle to a job interview! No wonder you’re unemployed. With the last guy I hit the jackpot. This god-like beautiful boy traveled across the whole country to this interview. I still can’t understand why doesn’t work as a model or something. After having a nice chat I told him about the job and the fee. And about the “other” option. Will you guess what got filled with cum?
title: Dirty Scout 08
